{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"style","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">Página inicial de referência do atributo SVG</a></p>\n\n<p>Este atributo especifica informação de estilo para o elemento atual. O atributo \"style\" especifica informação de estilo para um único elemento. As linguagem da folha de estilos para as regras de estilos em linhas é dada pelo valor do atributo <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/contentStyleType\">contentStyleType</a></code> no elemento the <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;SVG&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"Contexto de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Categorias</th>\n   <td>Atributo de apresentação</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Valor</th>\n   <td>&lt;style&gt;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animável?</th>\n   <td>Não</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Documento Normativo</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/styling.html#StyleAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2ª Edição)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"style\">&lt;style&gt;</dt>\n <dd>A sintaxe do estilo depende de uma linguagem de folha de estilos. Por padrão, se <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/contentStyleType\">contentStyleType</a></code> não for definido, a linguagem da folha de estilo utilizada será a CSS.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O exemplo a seguir mostra a estilização de um retângulo com um atributo de estilo utilizando a linguagem de folha de estilos do CSS.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewbox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 1000 500<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>600<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">fill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">stroke</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elementos","title":"Elementos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Os seguintes elementos podem utilizar o atributo <code>style</code></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#container\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Container\">Elementos \"container\"</a> »</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#filterprimitive\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#FilterPrimitive\">Elementos de filtro primitivo</a> »</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#gradient\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Gradient\">Elementos de gradiente</a> »</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#graphics\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Graphics\">Elementos gráficos</a> »</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#structural\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Structural\">Elementos estruturais</a> »</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#textcontent\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#TextContent\">Elementos de texto</a> »</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/clipPath\"><code>&lt;clipPath&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Contexto de uso","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Elementos","id":"elementos"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"« Página inicial de referência do atributo SVG","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"style","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"style","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"style","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/svg/attribute/style","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/svg/attribute/style/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Gráficos Vetoriais Escaláveis"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG Attribute reference"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style","title":"style"}],"pageTitle":"style - SVG: Gráficos